|0 |PX COORDINATOR           |        |100000  |686415      |
|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR     |:EX10000|100000  |598229      |
|2 |  └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR    |        |100000  |400000      |
|3 |    └─EXTERNAL TABLE SCAN|EX_T1   |100000  |400000      |
